data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this well maintained townhouse located in the sought-after Derry Township. The main level features an open floor plan with a recently updated kitchen and all-new flooring. Upstairs, two spacious bedrooms with en-suite baths and a convenient laundry area await. The walk-out lower level offers a partially finished space with ample storage. Enjoy the lifestyle of a well-cared-for home in a prime location. Schedule a showing today to make this your ideal living space.
